---

<MainLayout>
  <h2>About</h2>

  <div class="squarecontainer">
    <div class="square"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="videocontainer">
    <video class="video" controls>
      <source src="public/video/testvideo.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
    </video>
  </div>

  <div class="aboutsectioncontainer">
    <div class="squarecontainer2">
      <img src="public/img/falang-noi-marken.webp" alt="Photo" />
      <div class="square2"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="aboutsection">
      <h1 class="nanna">NANNA</h1>
      <h1>MALUMGON</h1>
      <p>
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consetetur sadipscing elitr, sed diam nonumy eirmod tempor invidunt ut labore et dolore magna aliquyam erat, sed diam voluptua. At
